maven 配置使用 nexus 私服 修改~/.m2/settings.xml内容如下：
 mvn config
&lt;?xml version=&#34;1.0&#34; encoding=&#34;UTF-8&#34;?&gt; &lt;settings xmlns=&#34;http://maven.apache.org/SETTINGS/1.0.0&#34; xmlns:xsi=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&#34; xsi:schemaLocation=&#34;http://maven.apache.org/SETTINGS/1.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/xsd/settings-1.0.0.xsd&#34;&gt; &lt;servers&gt; &lt;server&gt; &lt;id&gt;releases&lt;/id&gt; &lt;username&gt;admin&lt;/username&gt; &lt;password&gt;admin123&lt;/password&gt; &lt;/server&gt; &lt;server&gt; &lt;id&gt;snapshots&lt;/id&gt; &lt;username&gt;admin&lt;/username&gt; &lt;password&gt;admin123&lt;/password&gt; &lt;/server&gt; &lt;server&gt; &lt;id&gt;thirdpart&lt;/id&gt; &lt;username&gt;admin&lt;/username&gt; &lt;password&gt;admin123&lt;/password&gt; &lt;/server&gt; &lt;/servers&gt; &lt;mirrors&gt; &lt;mirror&gt; &lt;id&gt;central&lt;/id&gt; &lt;name&gt;central&lt;/name&gt; &lt;url&gt;http://localhost:8081/nexus/content/groups/public/&lt;/url&gt; &lt;mirrorOf&gt;*&lt;/mirrorOf&gt; &lt;/mirror&gt; &lt;/mirrors&gt; &lt;/settings&gt; 
